Every time you masturbate...God kills a kitten
[[Image:God-kills-kitten.jpg|thumb|The poor man's ceiling cat.]]

==Overview==
Every time you masturbate... God kills a kitten is an [[unfunny]] internet meme started [[last thursday]] by some [[faggot]] on [[Fark]] who just learned [[photoshop]] but not comedy. It is full of [[Fail]] and [[Aids]], and is an obvious copycat (pun intended) of the beloved [[Ceiling Cat]]. It is half as cute, a fifth as funny, and not original at all, therefore [[Shit_nobody_cares_about|it is the best and most popular thing Fark has ever generated]]; which proves how pathetic the site truly is.

==Wikipedia==
Proving once again how awful [[TOW]] really is, God kills a kitten actually has an [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Every_time_you_masturbate%2C_God_kills_a_kitten article on Wikipedia.]] Which shows how poorly made the site is. Well made articles are always being [[You_are_doing_it_wrong|nominated for deletion review]] yet shitty [[meme]] articles will continue to live.

==Popularity==
Due to it's inclusion of [[Domo-kun]] and a kitten, the image grew popularity amongst [[wapanese]] and [[furfags]]. Due to that fanbase it has been emailed [[Over 9000]] times and has [[Aids| spread to every person in the world]].

